FBIS3-16012 "drsov049_g_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-049 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Mar 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus Agreement Ratified WS1103202294 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 1815 GMT 11 Mar 94 WS1103202294 Minsk Radio Minsk Network Language: Belarusian Article Type:BFN [Text] An agreement on the coordination of activities in the military sphere has been ratified today at the Belarusian Foreign Ministry. According to the agreement, both sides assumed the obligation to cooperate in the military sphere and, in case of a military assault on either of them, hold mutual consultations. The agreement also provides for joint operations of Belarus and Russia with regard to training military cadre, ensuring social and legal guarantees for servicemen, and preservation of the present use of the communications system network. The sides agreed to support military settlements on a reciprocal basis.
